HEADWORD: Portland stone
<hw>Port"land stone"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A yellowish-white
calcareous freestone from the Isle of Portland in England, much used in
building.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

